[10.475686, "o", "\u001b[34m╭─\u001b[0m\u001b[34m \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34mWhat this does\u001b[0m\u001b[34m \u001b[0m\u001b[34m────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\u001b[0m\u001b[34m─╮\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[34m│\u001b[0m Shows disk space usage for the filesystem containing the current directory, with sizes displayed in human-readable   \u001b[34m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[34m│\u001b[0m units. It reports total, used, available space, usage percentage, and the mount point.                               \u001b[34m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[34m╰──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\u001b[0m\r\n"]
